::Kaiser::
       Immediately realizing his error he holsters one blaster and draws a 
scimitar to parry the oncoming Devilcat's slashes.  "Frankly, sir, I didn't 
know particularly well who you were."  He grunts and holsters his other 
weapon tossing a small concussion grenade down Perceptor's hole.  He then 
turns back to Devilcat.  "Now then, I assure you, you will not enjoy my full 
attention."

--part1_29.392cfe12.2b81b805_boundary
